---
import { SITE_TITLE } from '@lib/constants';
---

<footer class="bg-primary text-white mt-20 border-t border-primary-light">
  <div class="max-w-(--page-max-width) mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
      <!-- Brand -->
      <div>
        <p class="font-sans font-bold text-lg text-secondary mb-3">{SITE_TITLE}</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          BVI 英属维尔京群岛离岸工具全方位中文指南。<br />家族办公室策略平台。
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Quick Links -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-sans font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-400 mb-4">核心专题</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/spc/" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-secondary transition-colors">SPC</a></li>
          <li><a href="/bc/" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-secondary transition-colors">BC</a></li>
          <li><a href="/vista/" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-secondary transition-colors">VISTA</a></li>
          <li><a href="/ptc/" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-secondary transition-colors">PTC</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Tools -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-sans font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-400 mb-4">实用工具</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/bvi-2-0/" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-secondary transition-colors">BVI 2.0</a></li>
          <li><a href="/comparison/" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-secondary transition-colors">工具对比</a></li>
          <li><a href="/fees/" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-secondary transition-colors">费用一览</a></li>
          <li><a href="/calendar/" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-secondary transition-colors">合规日历</a></li>
          <li><a href="/case-studies/" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-secondary transition-colors">案例参考</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Info -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-sans font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-400 mb-4">信息</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/china-law/" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-secondary transition-colors">BVI.vg 与中国法律</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about/" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-secondary transition-colors">关于本站</a></li>
          <li><a href="/sources/" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-secondary transition-colors">官方资源导航</a></li>
          <li><a href="/faq/" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-secondary transition-colors">常见问题</a></li>
          <li><a href="/disclaimer/" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-secondary transition-colors">免责声明</a></li>
          <li><a href="/privacy/" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-secondary transition-colors">隐私政策</a></li>
          <li><a href="/terms/" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-secondary transition-colors">使用条款</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contact/" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-secondary transition-colors">联系方式</a></li>
          <li><a href="/search/" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-secondary transition-colors">搜索</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-primary-light mt-10 pt-6 text-center text-xs text-gray-400 space-y-1">
      <p>BVI.vg 是独立中文知识网站，与 BVI Government、BVI FSC、BVI ITA 等机构无隶属、授权或背书关系。</p>
      <p>本站内容仅供一般信息参考，不构成法律、税务、投资或监管意见。</p>
      <p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} {SITE_TITLE}</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>